## Quick Reference: Security Patterns

| Category | Safe Pattern |
|----------|-------------|
| Input Validation | `ALLOWED_OPS.includes(args.op)` |
| Number Validation | `parseInt(args.id, 10)` with `isNaN` check |
| String Sanitization | `str.replace(/[<>\"\'&]/g, '')` |
| Safe Logging | `console.log('Done:', args.data?.ticket?.id)` |
| Error Logging | `console.error('Failed:', e.message)` |
| Safe DOM | `el.textContent = data` |
| Sanitized HTML | `sanitizeHTML(data)` before innerHTML |
| Secret Storage | `$db.set('config', { ... })` |
| Masked Display | `'****' + key.slice(-4)` |
